        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ OSHC with Allianz (cheapest option). Used it for GP visits and a minor hospital procedure—no issues, fully covered. Working 25 hours/week covers rent. Planning to apply for Temporary Graduate Visa after completion.</p>
